‚ñ° City name in H1 and throughout content
‚ñ° Local landmarks or geographic references
‚ñ° Service area coverage mentioned
‚ñ° Local business hours and contact info
‚ñ° Driving directions or location context
‚ñ° Community involvement references

CONVERSION OPTIMIZATION:
